jan Ewalin li kama sona e sona jan lon tomo sona ⌈Arizona State University⌋. ona li kama sona e sona pi tomo lipu lon tomo sona ⌈Wayne State University⌋ lon ma tomo ⌈Detroit, Michigan⌋. ona li alasa e pali lon tomo lipu lon ma tomo suli ⌈Detroit⌋.
ona li pali e lawa ilo e sitelen linluwi e sitelen lipu lon tomo sewi ⌈Partnership Place⌋. ona li jan nasin lon kulupu pana ⌈Dungytreei Heritage Foundation⌋.
ona li musi e ilo musi ⌈Digimon⌋ e sona lon sitelen tawa ⌈South Park⌋ e sona nasin tan jan ⌈Hegel⌋.
o lukin e lipu pali ona.
